Target: `tests/DocumentIngestion.Tests.ps1`

Reason:
- add follow-up coverage for non-fatal cleanup visibility behavior introduced in the Priority 0 ingestion fixes
- document how to test warning-producing timeout/cleanup branches without requiring live Docling/Tika infrastructure

